name: team-tech-project-november
title: Team Tech Project: November
shortDescription: Form teams to build a project and share it with us the following month! Beginners welcome!
longDescription: Team Tech Project is a monthly meetup for club members interested in gaining experience working in a team, as well as building up their portfolio. Each month, participants get together to form teams, build awesome projects, and share what they built and learned the following month! No experience? No problem! We'll have plenty of resources and a few workshops in the coming weeks to get you up and running. If you ever get stuck on something, you can always ask for help on our Discord server!
